{"tid":1895730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺文宣2","createTime":"2020-02-24T17:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T17:48:16.000Z","uid":265964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"945fc568ce88e4b8a2a26ada89fbc41ed0ae5f50","tid":1895730,"uid":265964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:06:36.000Z","msg":"而家韓國 意大利大爆發<br />\n其實勁應該做外國文宣<br />\n鄰國人而家不停自我宣傳<br />\n話自己唔係病菌 話病菌係世界既問題<br />\n唔係佢地既錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地而家應該係要point out<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地先係病原體</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解而家全世界都會有？<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">因為係佢地傳出去既</span><br />\n而家微博係到嘈話要封韓仔關<br />\n所以要做韓國文宣話俾韓仔知<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">佢地帶菌傳俾你地後仲話自己係victim<br />\n搶曬你地既口罩仲話自己防疫做得好<br />\n反轉頭歧視韓仔 <br />\n證明班人只係一堆只會搶資源<br />\n然後害人地既撚樣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家應該狂幫twitter打<span style=\"color: violet;\">wuhan virus</span> 既戰線<br />\nHastag到而家一出肺炎新聞<br />\n大家都會諗到係邊條撚樣傳到全世界都係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">要將virus掛鈎到佢地身上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nN6gHbh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnN6gHbh.jpg&h=2b9eb64d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"555d22d2c0431c4ea7e11470a8693b08c1913c73","tid":1895730,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T17:20:46.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=e2dde8de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"04286d8e621b1fe0b9b9cfddcb2e2488767608da","tid":1895730,"uid":265964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T17:48:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}